title: Elbow Grease Antibacterial Wipes | Kills Cold & Flu Viruses (Kills 99.9% of Bacteria) - Grapefruit (80 pack)
features: KILLS 99.9% OF BACTERIA: Elbow Grease Antibacterial Wipes provide a hygienic deep clean, killing bacteria that can linger on surfaces. Perfect for wiping down kitchen counters or bathroom surfaces, they ensure your home or work stays safe and sanitised.

BIODEGRADABLE & PLASTIC-FREE: Each wipe is designed to break down naturally, helping to reduce waste and protect the environment. Made without plastic, these wipes let you clean your home responsibly, so you can feel good about every wipe.

80 WIPES PER PACK: Each pack includes 80 wipes, giving you plenty to tackle messes big and small. Keep a pack under the sink or in the glove box for cleaning emergencies and enjoy a long-lasting supply of freshness.

MULTIPURPOSE SURFACE WIPES: From kitchen worktops to bathroom tiles and even furniture, these wipes tackle multiple cleaning tasks. Use them around the home or take them on-the-go for a quick clean in the car or office.

CONVENIENT RESEALABLE PACK: The handy resealable pack keeps wipes moist and ready for action, every time you need them. Store easily in cupboards or bags and prevent the wipes from drying out between uses.
description: Product Description Elbow Grease Antibacterial Wipes are the ultimate solution for every household cleaning need. Packed with power, these plastic-free, biodegradable wipes are tough on germs yet kind to the planet. Designed to kill 99.9% of bacteria, they’re ideal for keeping your home hygienically spotless. Perfect for use on hobs, worktops, and furniture, these multipurpose wet wipes make cleaning quick and convenient in any room of your home. Each resealable pack includes 80 wipes, ensuring you always have a fresh wipe ready for action. Available in refreshing lemon or grapefruit scents, Elbow Grease wipes are an essential for every home, car, or office, helping you tackle life’s messes with ease and confidence. With Elbow Grease Antibacterial Wipes, deep cleaning becomes a breeze. From quick kitchen wipe-downs to full household cleans, these cleaning wipes are the go-to tool for anyone who values a tidy, germ-free space. The eco-friendly design means you can get a powerful clean without adding plastic waste to the planet. Choose Elbow Grease and discover the easy way to keep your home fresh and bacteria-free, day in and day out. Ingredients Didecyldimethyl Ammonium Chloride (0.5% w/w), <5% Anionic Surfactants, Non-Ionic Surfactants, Disinfectants, Parfum.
